-- Liverpool Hosts Arsenal on Opening Day of Premier League; Chelsea-WBA
-- Alex Duff
-- 2010-06-17T08:31:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-17/liverpool-hosts-arsenal-on-opening-day-of-premier-league-chelsea-wba.html

          
          
             Liverpool hosts Arsenal on the
opening day of the Premier League season. Defending champion
Chelsea and Manchester United host promoted teams West Bromwich
Albion and Newcastle, respectively.  
 Tottenham starts at home against Manchester City, while
Blackpool plays its first Premier League game at home to Wigan
Athletic. The games, scheduled for Aug. 14, were announced on
the league website today.  
          
          


  


        